3
00:00:04,797 --> 00:00:06,767
(Jung Gun Joo, Oh Woo Ri, Ko Chang Seok, Seo Young Hee)

4
00:00:06,807 --> 00:00:08,407
(And Shim Eun Kyung)

5
00:00:09,537 --> 00:00:12,977
(Way Back Love)

6
00:00:21,117 --> 00:00:22,416
(Danger)

7
00:00:22,417 --> 00:00:23,917
